{"tid":1848623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有人睇戲、有人食雞粥，冇一個地方係安全","createTime":"2020-01-28T14:33:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T16:52:11.000Z","uid":63154,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"932e45c1378edec32f0199cbd796e77a151b8d23","tid":1848623,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:33:30.000Z","msg":"你仲返工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"985a44d742557f1b65dd5e485a02340094b6d32a","tid":1848623,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:35:31.000Z","msg":"全港死撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f8fa56e4d55b4256c8c56ecf605cbe7533de49","tid":1848623,"uid":149862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:36:08.000Z","msg":"準備嚟緊呢個月都留係屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83c1b6f5e71765c9334765681e11f430aa8e2624","tid":1848623,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:37:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">除咗醫護之外<br />\n垃圾政府都推緊社福界去死</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">學校停 康文設施都停<br />\n啲人就湧晒去唔停嘅中心<br />\n社區爆發岌岌可危<br />\n<br />\n<ins>要求立即停止所有非緊急服務</ins></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845195\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845195</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AS4YPwC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAS4YPwC.jpg&h=a350fa60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"00e2e0cf113c812293efbdc7c105f252724c1110","tid":1848623,"uid":63697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:37:28.000Z","msg":"封關+等潛伏期後冇事先係最安全"},{"pid":"35d8fee684fe745831e159c00ffd3b90c3ace060","tid":1848623,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:37:39.000Z","msg":"嗰啲唔撚係人<br />\n係畜牲！"},{"pid":"3030a2e27973c3847800b42bc07701fcfaad8abd","tid":1848623,"uid":240962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:37:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a93db2d800363b0885a866a3e7e382cb86ab8b6","tid":1848623,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:38:44.000Z","msg":"屋企最安全"},{"pid":"9d19665dcb224e70ce6419627c4c6c12020aa8c8","tid":1848623,"uid":344033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:45:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請廣傳</span></span><br />\n<br />\n手足裝備抗沙士：防毒面具/濾罐 (型號/分析/用法/清潔全齊）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1848447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1848447</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n整體分析圖：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F116690396531818%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=3dcf6aaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n</a><br />\n個別仔細分析：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">護目鏡</span>：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845419</a></span></span> / <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F117867026414155%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=0757c01d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\nVPN 大踢爆：<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=112386483628876&amp;id=112357283631796&amp;__tn__=%2As-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D112386483628876%26id%3D112357283631796%26__tn__%3D%252As-R&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=ffb071a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=112386483628876&amp;id=112357283631796&amp;__tn__=%2As-R</a><br />\n<br />\n請大家廣傳，避免沉底<br />\n<br />\n最近口罩同N95 都賣曬，部分手足屋企口罩已經就黎用盡，今日同大家介紹下可以防沙士+TG嘅濾罐同濾棉。第一，係for 用曬/買唔到口罩嘅手足，第二係希望方便大家一次過買齊發夢+出街嘅裝備，就算沙士完左，自用送禮都可以繼續名貴大方。<br />\n<br />\nN95/R95/P95 口罩基本上係particulate respirator, 外科口罩防嘅係飛沫粒子，即係我地用防毒面具代替，就要裝particulate filter，換言之，就係濾棉！<br />\n<br />\n濾棉最高級別就係P100，防油性+非油性粒子，即係TG（油性）同埋病毒都可以防，型號包括2091, 2097, 2297, 6035（只有英國製）,7093 等等，而60926等等嘅6092X 系列濾罐，因為內置P100 濾棉，所以一樣ok <br />\n其中，6053 同 7093 棉係防水的，清潔消毒會較方便，而60926表面亦有膠盒。<br />\n<br />\n有強國人做過測試，係北京霧霾毒氣之下，3M 2091 用左十一日過濾能力都係跌左1%，手足請自行考慮幾耐換一次。<br />\n<br />\nAmazon 大log買亦有便，大家可以組團買。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.3m.com.au/3M/en_AU/company-au/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3/?N=5002385+8711017+3294471754&amp;rt=rud\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3m.com.au%2F3M%2Fen_AU%2Fcompany-au%2Fall-3m-products%2F~%2F3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3%2F%3FN%3D5002385%2B8711017%2B3294471754%26rt%3Drud&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=a22bb741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.3m.com.au/3M/en_AU/company-au/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3/?N=5002385+8711017+3294471754&amp;rt=rud</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.3m.com/3M/en_US/company-us/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case/?N=5002385+3294776429&amp;rt=rud\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3m.com%2F3M%2Fen_US%2Fcompany-us%2Fall-3m-products%2F~%2F3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case%2F%3FN%3D5002385%2B3294776429%26rt%3Drud&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=bd1c2fc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.3m.com/3M/en_US/company-us/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case/?N=5002385+3294776429&amp;rt=rud</a><br />\n<br />\n2003 年沙士，淘大嘅清理人員就係用2091棉+600X 罐（罐理論上唔洗，應該係防佢地嘅清潔同消毒藥水）。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">如何清潔防毒面具可參考依段片，有教disinfection，主要都係漂白水同消毒劑<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dE5IweYn3T4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdE5IweYn3T4&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=3fc18907\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dE5IweYn3T4</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n清潔步驟：<br />\n入到屋企唔好除裝備住，用酒精紙巾抹左面具同濾棉/罐表面先，跟住抹埋手再洗手（點解又要酒精又要洗手係有原因的），跟住就除面罩，再跟番片入面嘅教學清潔<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n防毒面具方面，建議大家買/用6800 或者其他包曬成塊面嘅款式，咁樣就唔洗帶眼罩，一舊野保護曬成塊面，最安全。因為你戴半面+眼罩，咁就多舊野清潔，同埋部分眼罩封唔曬，冇咁安全。<br />\n<br />\n型號方面，全面嘅建議大家買6800，順便擋埋橡膠子彈，半面嘅就買7502/ 6500，兩款手足都表示舒適度幾高。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112044766987392/posts/119490526242816/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112044766987392%2Fposts%2F119490526242816%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=7a5973a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112044766987392/posts/119490526242816/?d=n</a><br />\n酒精搓手液 vs 洗手梘液</span>"},{"pid":"4fb4f0680930160b9fd044333599f2d3f296e929","tid":1848623,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T16:39:38.000Z","msg":"除左快閃落買嘢食都唔會出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d675cc3d75adda3b3374c0299cc5d95436df1f1","tid":1848623,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35d8fee684fe745831e159c00ffd3b90c3ace060","tid":1848623,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:37:39.000Z","msg":"嗰啲唔撚係人<br />\n係畜牲！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T16:52:11.000Z","msg":"支那賤種先會有病周圍走"}]}